          "process_md": "**Step 1:** The applicant’s parent or guardian must visit the nearest Anganwadi Centre (AWC).\n**Step 2:** The Anganwadi Worker (AWW) will verify the child’s age and nutritional status.\n**Step 3:** On confirmation of SUW or MAM status, the child will be enrolled under MSPY for a duration of 75 days.\n**Step 4:** Distribution of Nutrition Support:\n\n  - The 75-day nutrition support after enrolment.\n  - Hot Cooked Meals under SNP,\n  - Besan Atta Premix (monthly),\n  - Eggs and Bananas (weekly).\n\n**Step 5:** Anganwadi Workers conduct regular home visits, provide counselling, and monitor progress at the Anganwadi Centre.\n<br>\n\n"
        }
